data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Tranquility and modern comfort meet in perfect harmony. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this  home offers a private backyard next to the Goose Creek Reservoir. New granite countertops in kitchen and bathrooms, LVP flooring on first floor, new refrigerator and dishwasher. The roof is new 2019, Lennox HVAC 2021. New dual flush toilets in each bathroom. round out the upgrades.Freshly painted and exterior pressure washed, the back porch features a delightful pergola, offering the perfect spot to relax and unwind while enjoying the tranquil ambiance and views of the surrounding landscape. For those environmentally conscious and tech-savvy, a convenient 240-volt outlet awaits, ready to charge your electric vehicle. Don't miss this opportunity to call 1021 Steelchase Ln your home. Schedule a showing today, Your dream home awaits!
